  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3533520/extras/808f82bbb3d1f57f84d59d3739bf3d4e.webp?t=1742479927\" width=32 height=32 /></span>On a deserted island, you are trying to survive amidst unknown creatures and dangers. Facing hunger, thirst, and deadly threats, you must hunt, craft powerful weapons, and find a way to escape. But the dangers are not only from the wild…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you survive on this challenging island? In Accursed Isle: Survival, become a true hunter against nature and unknown threats, and find the way out!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get the early access version to gain great advantages and support us.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3533520/extras/808f82bbb3d1f57f84d59d3739bf3d4e.webp?t=1742479927\" width=32 height=32 /></span>On a deserted island, you are trying to survive amidst unknown creatures and dangers. Facing hunger, thirst, and deadly threats, you must hunt, craft powerful weapons, and find a way to escape. But the dangers are not only from the wild…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you survive on this challenging island? In Accursed Isle: Survival, become a true hunter against nature and unknown threats, and find the way out!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get the early access version to gain great advantages and support us.</p>",
